title: This Week in Highlights | 3/13/17
description: Personal Branding & Storytelling: In this week's compilation we highlight my journey as a 'personal brand,' the influence that Walt Disney and Vince McMahon had on me and the nature of storytelling, my time spent with Shonduras and Tanner Fox (two massive personal brands), and what it really takes to win in today's digital society ;)
